{"TopicId":128610,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Battle Mech 100% Stock","CreatedByName":"Arron Rift","CreatedById":113722,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T07:45:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Arron Rift","CreatedById":113722,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T07:45:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalx.com/Arron_Rift/Battle-Mech-100-stock\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalx.com/Arron_Rift/Battle-Mech-100-stock\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/359525062629735084/2C1FD65CA8A902457513290B3AB4D3FB8B18749A/\u0022 alt=\u00222C1FD65CA8A902457513290B3AB4D3FB8B18749A\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/359525062629738977/12801E121A4D7E4D4FD18642DC70B4D0B15727A6/\u0022 alt=\u002212801E121A4D7E4D4FD18642DC70B4D0B15727A6\u0022\u003EHey guys, this is the first creation I\u0027ve ever posted here, I hope you like it \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe description in the save file gives usage instructions. It sort of \u0022skates\u0022 with the wheels on its feet. The autopilot can generally keep it upright, especially on moons. It\u0027s not necessarily practical, but it is a LOT of fun to drive \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith its ion engines I was able to land on the mun when launched from 80,000m above Kerbin. I recommend using it with Hyperedit (or at least quicksaving before undocking the mech in case it falls over) but I included a launch-cage in the craft for mounting on a rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy, and Merry Christmas everyone \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XB-70A","CreatedById":144985,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T15:04:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerfect to annihilate some clanners.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Planetfall","CreatedById":154594,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T15:07:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat thing looks really nice. I love\u00A0the the level of detail you put into it, the Kerbal\u0027s head sticking out is cute. XP\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMarry Christmas\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Arron Rift","CreatedById":113722,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-12-25T18:49:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222336204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022128610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221451056037\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154594\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Planetfall\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Planetfall said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat thing looks really nice. I love\u00A0the the level of detail you put into it, the Kerbal\u0027s head sticking out is cute. XP\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMarry Christmas\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-up